.el .ds Aq '
.TH devin-cloud-drs-help 1  "help " 
.SH NAME
devin\-cloud\-drs\-help \- Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdevin cloud drs help\fR [\fIsubcommands\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
devin\-cloud\-drs\-help\-whoami(1)
Print the current DRS configuration (org, API endpoint, auth status)
.TP
devin\-cloud\-drs\-help\-sandbox\-create(1)
Create a sandbox Devin session for testing repo setup
.TP
devin\-cloud\-drs\-help\-run(1)
Run a shell command inside a sandbox session
.TP
devin\-cloud\-drs\-help\-blueprint\-list(1)
List all environment blueprints for the organization
.TP
devin\-cloud\-drs\-help\-blueprint\-create(1)
Create a new environment blueprint
.TP
devin\-cloud\-drs\-help\-blueprint\-write(1)
Update an existing environment blueprint
.TP
devin\-cloud\-drs\-help\-build(1)
Trigger an environment build and wait for it to finish
.TP
devin\-cloud\-drs\-help\-build\-start(1)
Trigger an environment build without waiting
.TP
devin\-cloud\-drs\-help\-build\-wait(1)
Wait for a previously started build to finish
.TP
devin\-cloud\-drs\-help\-build\-logs(1)
Fetch the log stream for a build job
.TP
devin\-cloud\-drs\-help\-secret\-create(1)
Create an organization\-level secret
.TP
devin\-cloud\-drs\-help\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
